OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FHeavy
OL,6,Fshowers persisting across Cornwall
OL,7,Fthis evening before easing. Elsewhere
OL,8,Flargely dry with the clearest skies in
OL,9,Fthe east, cloudier elsewhere. Further
OL,10,Fshowers arriving into the far west by
OL,11,Fdawn. Chilly in the east.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FA mostly dry albeit cloudy
OL,14,Fday with a few showers around, these
OL,15,Fmainly in the north. Best of the
OL,16,Fsunshine confined to the south coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
