OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FHeavy,
OL,6,Fslow moving showers likely on Friday
OL,7,Fwith longer spells of rain arriving
OL,8,Ffrom the south on Saturday into Sunday
OL,9,Fbefore clearing. Turning warmer and
OL,10,Fmore humid on Saturday.
